'''2021年'''2月23日，'''[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]'''的三個'''[[监狱|监狱]]'''发生'''骚乱'''，造成至少75名囚犯死亡<ref>{{Cite web|title=厄瓜多尔监狱暴乱死亡人数增至75人|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-02/24/c_1127133388.htm|access-date=2021-02-24|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224094646/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-02/24/c_1127133388.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。厄瓜多爾当局将其归咎于过度拥挤的三个监狱中发生的帮派争斗<ref>{{Cite news|author=Afp|date=2021-02-24|title=At least 75 inmates dead in Ecuador prison riots|language=en|work=The Hindu|url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/at-least-75-inmates-dead-in-ecuador-prison-riots/article33920019.ece|accessdate=2021-02-24|issn=0971-751X|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225180229/https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/at-least-75-inmates-dead-in-ecuador-prison-riots/article33920019.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這三个监狱分別位于[[瓜亚斯省|瓜亚斯省]]、[[阿苏艾省|阿苏艾省]]和[[科托帕希省|科托帕希省]]，3個監獄內的人口占据了该国监狱总人口的近70%<ref>{{Cite web|title=At least 62 killed in Ecuadorean prison gang riots|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/world/ecuador-prison-gang-riots-deaths-7202099/|accessdate=2021-02-24|date=2021-02-24|work=The Indian Express|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225144535/https://indianexpress.com/article/world/ecuador-prison-gang-riots-deaths-7202099/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。為控制监狱暴力，厄瓜多爾總統[[利寧·莫雷諾|利寧·莫雷諾]]宣布該國的监狱系统进入临时紧急状态<ref>{{Cite web|title=62 Inmates Dead In Ecuador Prison Riots|url=https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/62-inmates-dead-in-ecuador-prison-riots-2377234|accessdate=2021-02-24|work=NDTV.com|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224220544/https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/62-inmates-dead-in-ecuador-prison-riots-2377234|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

